label: ID
desc: non identifiable randomly generated character id.

label: Alias
desc: another way to call the character.

label: Love Rank
desc: love rank based in users preference.

label: Hate Rank
desc: hate rank based in users preference.

label: Tags
desc: comma separated list of tags for this character.

label: Loves
desc: how many users love this character.

label: Hates
desc: how many users hate this character.

label: Description
desc: short text with description if this character.

label: Anime Planet URL
desc: url to the main page of character in Anime Planet.

label: User Preference
desc: True if the user loves the character, False if he hates it.
